00:13:20,978 --> 00:13:25,679
Mr. Joestar, when you asked me to help
get your grandson out of this jail cell,

253
00:13:25,704 --> 00:13:28,261
I had planned on going easy on the boy,

254
00:13:28,286 --> 00:13:31,985
but in light of his tremendous
power, I'm reconsidering that.

255
00:13:32,264 --> 00:13:35,123
Just one misstep could put us all in danger.

256
00:13:35,148 --> 00:13:36,627
Tell me if you want me to stop.

257
00:13:36,652 --> 00:13:41,222
If not, I'll resort to a use of force
that could land your grandson in the hospital.

258
00:13:41,291 --> 00:13:43,570
Like I said, do what you gotta do.

259
00:13:44,007 --> 00:13:45,090
Yes, sir!

260
00:13:46,738 --> 00:13:48,648
Red bind!

261
00:13:50,177 --> 00:13:51,375
Huh? What the...

262
00:13:57,470 --> 00:13:58,594
What's up with this heat?

263
00:13:58,619 --> 00:14:01,160
Yeah, what the hell's going
on? None of this makes any sense!

264
00:14:01,185 --> 00:14:04,036
Papa, that's enough! What are you doing to Jotaro?

265
00:14:04,061 --> 00:14:08,618
Holly, be a good girl, and let
papa finish what he started, okay?

266
00:14:08,643 --> 00:14:10,219
I can't breathe.

267
00:14:11,148 --> 00:14:13,087
The evil spirit is withdrawing.

268
00:14:13,112 --> 00:14:15,091
The heat is restricting his breathing,

269
00:14:15,116 --> 00:14:17,616
which causes the evil spirit to weaken.

270
00:14:17,688 --> 00:14:19,079
And now for the truth.

271
00:14:19,290 --> 00:14:22,288
This may seem like an evil spirit, but it's far from it.

272
00:14:22,719 --> 00:14:23,558
Jotaro,

273
00:14:23,719 --> 00:14:29,826
this thing you believe has possessed you is actually
a powerful vision created by your own life energy.

274
00:14:30,073 --> 00:14:33,303
This vision will always appear standing by your side,

275
00:14:33,443 --> 00:14:35,557
and because of that, we call it...

276
00:14:35,582 --> 00:14:36,875
A stand!

277
00:14:37,932 --> 00:14:39,331
A stand?

278
00:14:39,475 --> 00:14:41,418
Remember Aesop's fable.

279
00:14:41,711 --> 00:14:44,798
The cold wind made the traveler pull his coat tighter,

280
00:14:44,934 --> 00:14:47,268
but the heat forced him to admit defeat.

281
00:14:47,377 --> 00:14:50,180
Ready to leave your cage now, JoJo?

282
00:14:51,242 --> 00:14:53,585
I said it before. I'm stayin'.

283
00:14:54,046 --> 00:14:57,185
I keep hurting other people
without even knowing I'm doing it.

284
00:14:57,457 --> 00:15:00,077
Until that stops, I'm stayin' here.

285
00:15:00,393 --> 00:15:02,319
It's nice to meet someone like me,

286
00:15:02,465 --> 00:15:04,058
but if you keep this up,

287
00:15:05,169 --> 00:15:06,486
you'll die.

288
00:15:12,954 --> 00:15:13,787
Huh?

289
00:15:14,149 --> 00:15:16,062
He just broke the damn toilet.

290
00:15:16,087 --> 00:15:18,343
Hey, that's destruction of property!

291
00:15:21,710 --> 00:15:23,401
You had your chance.

292
00:15:25,795 --> 00:15:27,230
All right, bastard.

293
00:15:27,374 --> 00:15:29,226
Don't say I didn't warn you.

294
00:15:43,967 --> 00:15:45,026
What the hell?

295
00:15:45,245 --> 00:15:47,447
Why'd you suddenly turn your back on me?

296
00:15:47,543 --> 00:15:48,556
We're not done.

297
00:15:49,589 --> 00:15:52,645
Mr. Joestar, he's left his jail cell.

298
00:15:52,726 --> 00:15:55,369
I've accomplished what you asked me to do, right?

299
00:16:05,400 --> 00:16:07,591
So now what? You got me, huh?

300
00:16:07,862 --> 00:16:09,118
Not exactly.

301
00:16:09,182 --> 00:16:12,445
I did have every intention of sending you to the hospital,

302
00:16:12,779 --> 00:16:14,812
but you're stronger than I had expected.

303
00:16:15,012 --> 00:16:17,523
And if I had kept going with this steel rod,

304
00:16:18,001 --> 00:16:19,692
just what would you have done?

305
00:16:19,839 --> 00:16:22,940
Do not underestimate my stand, Magician's Red.

306
00:16:23,183 --> 00:16:27,207
It could have easily melted that
rod midair into a worthless puddle.

307
00:16:27,232 --> 00:16:30,605
The power Avdol has is exactly the same as yours.

308
00:16:32,597 --> 00:16:35,669
If you want to know more about this evil spirit,

309
00:16:35,694 --> 00:16:37,742
you'll need to leave this jail.

310
00:16:47,221 --> 00:16:49,375
Thank you. Thank you, Jotaro.

311
00:16:49,503 --> 00:16:52,481
I'm glad you finally left that awful jail cell.

312
00:16:52,509 --> 00:16:54,991
Why are you such an annoying bitch?

313
00:16:55,016 --> 00:16:56,667
Okay. I don't know.

314
00:16:56,692 --> 00:16:59,527
Hey, how dare you address your own mother that way?!

315
00:16:59,552 --> 00:17:01,243
And what kind of language is that?

316
00:17:01,268 --> 00:17:04,238
And stop smiling, Holly. You'll only encourage it.

317
00:17:04,263 --> 00:17:05,230
Okay.

318
00:17:05,522 --> 00:17:07,563
Hey, grampa, one question.

319
00:17:07,929 --> 00:17:10,947
There's something that I can't quite wrap my brain around.

320
00:17:11,257 --> 00:17:13,276
You seem to know all about this...

321
00:17:13,301 --> 00:17:16,366
Evil spirit, the stand, whatever you wanna call it,

322
00:17:16,743 --> 00:17:17,965
but how do you know this?

323
00:17:17,990 --> 00:17:20,458
Hmm. How do I know?

324
00:17:20,554 --> 00:17:24,193
I guess I did come all the way
from New York to explain it to you.

325
00:17:24,218 --> 00:17:28,648
But in order for you to fully understand the
whole history of it, I must start from the beginning.

326
00:17:28,745 --> 00:17:31,783
This is part of the legacy of the Joestar family.

327
00:17:32,763 --> 00:17:34,766
Take a look at these pictures.

328
00:17:38,371 --> 00:17:39,795
What are these about?

329
00:17:39,856 --> 00:17:45,950
That coffin's a hundred years old, and four years ago,
it was pulled out of the Atlantic off the coast of Africa.

330
00:17:46,239 --> 00:17:47,263
Okay. So?

331
00:17:47,288 --> 00:17:48,892
I did a little research.

332
00:17:49,055 --> 00:17:53,864
My grandfather, Jonathan Joestar, your
great-grandfather, died while at sea.

333
00:17:54,136 --> 00:17:58,956
Turns out this exact same coffin
was on that boat with him when he died.

334
00:18:00,220 --> 00:18:03,739
When they discovered it four years ago, it was empty.

335
00:18:03,969 --> 00:18:06,933
But I know exactly what was inside it.

336
00:18:06,958 --> 00:18:10,119
Avdol and I are trying to locate him as we speak.

337
00:18:10,169 --> 00:18:12,073
Hold on. Did you say, "him"?

338
00:18:12,291 --> 00:18:15,307
Are you suggesting there was a person inside that thing?

339
00:18:15,603 --> 00:18:19,569
Come on. How could a human being stay
buried underwater for a hundred years?

340
00:18:19,609 --> 00:18:21,776
Because that person is evil incarnate,

341
00:18:21,984 --> 00:18:23,731
and his name is Dio!

342
00:18:23,803 --> 00:18:27,130
And now that he has been awakened
from his hundred-year slumber,

343
00:18:27,155 --> 00:18:30,109
it is our fate to fight that man!

344
00:18:32,522 --> 00:18:34,501
What the hell does that face mean?

345
00:18:34,526 --> 00:18:38,135
And don't you turn your back on me
like this has nothing to do with you!

346
00:18:38,239 --> 00:18:42,718
Look, you old man, this face means your
story is so lame, I don't know what to say.

347
00:18:42,743 --> 00:18:44,372
What? "Old man"?

348
00:18:44,578 --> 00:18:45,810
Avdol, was it?

349
00:18:46,019 --> 00:18:49,284
I don't know you, but you are one arrogant bastard.

350
00:18:49,710 --> 00:18:50,994
And as for you, old man...

351
00:18:51,019 --> 00:18:51,391
Huh?

352
00:18:51,597 --> 00:18:55,638
Did you really expect me to fall
for an unbelievable story like that?

353
00:18:55,663 --> 00:18:59,073
Heh. I know the story sounds far-fetched,

354
00:18:59,113 --> 00:19:03,624
but wouldn't you also say our evil
spirits are equally unbelievable?

355
00:19:05,397 --> 00:19:06,588
Think what you want,

356
00:19:06,636 --> 00:19:09,440
but soon you will have no choice but to believe it.

357
00:19:09,465 --> 00:19:14,103
If you want me to tell you how I know that
Dio exists and why I've chosen to go after him,

358
00:19:14,143 --> 00:19:16,517
the best way to explain it is to show you.

359
00:19:17,852 --> 00:19:23,541
See, the truth of it is I myself had a rather
startling revelation that prompted all of this.

360
00:19:23,566 --> 00:19:26,957
About a year ago, I suddenly obtained a stand of my own.

361
00:19:26,982 --> 00:19:28,275
What did you say?!

362
00:19:28,300 --> 00:19:29,817
Gramps, what did you...

363
00:19:31,138 --> 00:19:32,562
Get ready.

364
00:19:32,587 --> 00:19:33,888
Let me introduce...

365
00:19:34,456 --> 00:19:36,015
My stand!

366
00:19:44,215 --> 00:19:47,446
Did you see it, the thorns that came out of my hand?

367
00:19:47,520 --> 00:19:48,997
This is my stand.

368
00:19:49,022 --> 00:19:52,476
It can reveal faraway visions and place them on film.

369
00:19:52,501 --> 00:19:56,966
The only downside is I have to bust a
30,000-yen camera every time I use it!

370
00:19:56,991 --> 00:19:59,761
Excuse me. Is everything all right here?

371
00:19:59,786 --> 00:20:02,049
We're fine. Now go on. Run along.

372
00:20:02,108 --> 00:20:03,309
Of course.

373
00:20:03,541 --> 00:20:07,927
In a matter of seconds, a vision
will appear in this photograph, Jotaro,

374
00:20:07,952 --> 00:20:10,744
and it will reveal your very destiny!

375
00:20:10,831 --> 00:20:12,451
What are you talking about?

376
00:20:12,650 --> 00:20:14,152
Jotaro, Holly,

377
00:20:14,215 --> 00:20:18,996
have either of you ever taken the time to
look carefully at the back of your necks?

378
00:20:19,430 --> 00:20:20,846
What does that mean?

379
00:20:21,029 --> 00:20:24,463
You each have it, but you
probably never thought much about it,

380
00:20:24,488 --> 00:20:26,663
a birthmark shaped like a star.

381
00:20:26,688 --> 00:20:28,949
It turns out that we all have it.

382
00:20:32,287 --> 00:20:35,084
I'll say it again. What the hell does all this mean?

383
00:20:35,109 --> 00:20:40,551
My father died when I was young, so I asked my
mother about it, and she said he had one, too.

384
00:20:40,576 --> 00:20:45,730
It seems that everyone from the Joestar
bloodline is born with this exact same birthmark.

385
00:20:45,755 --> 00:20:49,942
All right, and just what the hell
is gonna turn up in that photograph?

386
00:20:49,967 --> 00:20:53,420
It's our destiny, a path that until now has been unknown.

387
00:20:53,445 --> 00:20:53,629
Papa.

388
00:20:53,654 --> 00:20:57,338
I'm losing my patience. Just
show me the damn photo already.

389
00:21:03,546 --> 00:21:06,879
Dio. He shows up in all my spirit photos,

390
00:21:07,110 --> 00:21:09,119
and look what's just above his shoulder.

391
00:21:09,445 --> 00:21:11,815
From the neck of this bastard on down

392
00:21:11,887 --> 00:21:14,833
is Jonathan Joestar, my grandfather!

393
00:21:14,858 --> 00:21:18,057
This son of a bitch took over his body!

394
00:21:20,323 --> 00:21:23,589
A hundred years ago, there was
an incident in the Atlantic ocean.

395
00:21:23,740 --> 00:21:26,899
All I know is what I've learned
from my grandmother, Erina.

396
00:21:26,924 --> 00:21:30,648
Somehow, Dio took over the body
of my grandfather and survived.

397
00:21:31,214 --> 00:21:33,216
And this much I know is certain...

398
00:21:33,425 --> 00:21:36,473
This bastard is currently hiding somewhere on the globe,

399
00:21:36,678 --> 00:21:37,919
plotting something.

400
00:21:38,759 --> 00:21:40,720
It's four years since he's revived,

401
00:21:40,745 --> 00:21:43,095
and the reason my spirit photography

402
00:21:43,262 --> 00:21:48,490
and your evil spirit have manifested
since is most likely connected to Dio.

403
00:21:48,515 --> 00:21:52,825
To society in general, our gifts
are considered a kind of psychic power.

404
00:21:53,044 --> 00:21:58,386
I've had my stand since the day I was
born, but your powers seem bound to Dio's body,

405
00:21:58,629 --> 00:22:01,296
or, rather, Jonathan Joestar's body.

406
00:22:01,321 --> 00:22:04,648
There's some sort of invisible
string that connects you all to him.

407
00:22:04,673 --> 00:22:08,778
His rebirth is also your own,
awakening your sleeping powers.

408
00:22:09,509 --> 00:22:14,014
Avdol, does this photograph give you
any indication to where he might be now?

409
00:22:15,167 --> 00:22:16,328
No, nothing.

410
00:22:16,384 --> 00:22:18,762
There's hardly anything of note in the photo at all.

411
00:22:19,140 --> 00:22:20,228
I see.

412
00:22:20,691 --> 00:22:22,707
I'll take a closer look later.

413
00:22:22,915 --> 00:22:24,249
Thank you. Hmm?

414
00:22:25,774 --> 00:22:26,981
Oh, Holly.

415
00:22:27,194 --> 00:22:29,913
I'm sorry I sprang this all on you out of the blue.

416
00:22:29,938 --> 00:22:31,310
Let's head home now.

417
00:22:31,469 --> 00:22:32,528
All right.

418
00:22:32,553 --> 00:22:35,307
I think I'll be sticking around for quite some time.

419
00:22:35,332 --> 00:22:37,734
You mind if I stay at your place while I'm here?

420
00:22:37,759 --> 00:22:41,029
No, of course not, papa. Let's go, Jotaro.

421
00:22:53,963 --> 00:22:55,310
Again...

422
00:22:56,296 --> 00:22:57,404
Just now...

423
00:22:57,429 --> 00:23:01,914
A most intense feeling like
someone somewhere is watching me.

424
00:23:02,771 --> 00:23:05,361
It is Jonathan's descendants.

425
00:23:05,430 --> 00:23:10,668
This body is sending out some kind
of spiritual signal to his offspring.

426
00:23:11,567 --> 00:23:14,553
Fine. It must be my fate.

427
00:23:15,376 --> 00:23:18,417
But fate must be purged.

428
00:23:19,824 --> 00:23:20,881
It's all set.

429
00:23:20,906 --> 00:23:23,377
I've taken the first step.

